                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Antonio Celeri <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uiti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> Iulia <lb n="3"/>Maxsima <note>sic</note> heres fecit <lb n="4"/>sibi et coniugi caro suo <expan><abbr>st</abbr><ex>ipendiorum</ex></expan> XXX <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">in</supplied> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ronte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> XII in <expan><abbr>ag</abbr><ex>ro</ex></expan> XVII
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erster Aufbewahrungsort: Stra (Italien). Oberhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines bewaffneten Reiters, darüber weibliche Büste. Datierung: nicht vor 42. n. Chr., als die legio VII die Beinamen Claudia pia fidelis erhielt.</p>
